description:
In one of his most focused talks to date, Stephen Ray discusses salvation, the authentic biblical understanding of being &quot;born again&quot;, and how we are indeed saved by faith, but not &quot;faith alone&quot;. With great humor and doctrinal depth, he goes all the way back to Abraham to show that we are saved by faith AND obedience to all that Christ demands of us.

